description:
This video was captured 3 years ago. Grandma Mita was visiting NZ. She had some fun bonding with her grandkids thru a sword play... "Thanks Mita for your moves! Salamat po..." 
We always have a great laugh watching this video. It was such a blessing having her and I hope you guys will be blessed too :)

 "A merry heart doeth good like a medicine but a broken spirit drieth the bones."
